  "status": "Final",
  "summary": "This ERC proposes a new standard for non-fungible tokens (NFTs) that supports multiple owners. The MO-NFT standard allows a single NFT to have multiple owners, reflecting the shared and distributable nature of digital assets. This model incorporates mechanisms for provider-defined transfer fees and ownership archiving, enabling flexible and collaborative ownership structures. It maintains compatibility with the existing [ERC-721](./eip-721.md) standard to ensure interoperability with current tools and platforms.",
  "title": "Multi-Owner Non-Fungible Tokens (MO-NFT)"
